      "type": "String",
      "label": "Description",
      "value": "<p>You calm your targetâ€™s mind, allowing them to think clearly. The target ignores any negative modifiers to their mental processes, such as Conditions like @Condition[Stunned], Mental Mutations, Psychologies, and so forth while the spell is in effect.</p><p><strong>Lore:</strong> You may inflict one @Condition[Blinded] Condition on those targeted by Lore of Light spells, unless they possess the Arcane Magic (Light) Talent. If a target has the @UUID[Compendium.wfrp4e-core.items.v3uzEthcq0JRar0J]{Daemonic} or @UUID[Compendium.wfrp4e-core.items.PFTD9gDvRWW9uh5g]{Undead} Creature Traits, spells also inflict an additional hit with Damage equal to your Intelligence Bonus that ignores Toughness Bonus and Armor Points.</p><p></p>"
